{"tid":354252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美少女失蹤　家人擔心被迫賣淫盼協尋","createTime":"2017-08-10T09:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T09:57:48.000Z","uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"10e5dc14ca62cf5b04102ba2019d861042b6c458","tid":354252,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>美少女失蹤　家人擔心被迫賣淫盼協尋</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170810/640_940cb5596168fb9af95684881d3c789a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170810%2F640_940cb5596168fb9af95684881d3c789a.jpg&h=00c17838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國加州聖馬刁郡（San Mateo County）一名16歲少女7月18日到學校參加暑期課程後就失蹤，家屬擔心她遭帶走被迫賣淫，盼社會大眾協尋，把她帶回家。<br />\n<br />\n16歲的曼多薩（Tays Mendoza）是西班牙裔，她擁有黑色頭髮和棕色眼睛，她的身高約為5尺3吋（約160公分），體重約180磅（約81公斤）。<br />\n<br />\n據失蹤兒童網站資訊，她目前可能在奧克蘭、海沃德（Hayward）、里奇蒙（Richmond）或舊金山，身邊有一名男子或一名女子作伴。<br />\n<br />\n家屬擔心她被拐走後被迫賣淫，已經向東帕羅奧圖（Palo Alto）及奧克蘭警局報案。家屬正盡全力尋找曼多薩，他們希望民眾如果看見她或有她的下落，請盡快與聖馬刁郡警長辦公聯絡。（盧宥竹／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"eea29b95e54876a76b8d79a407dcb60c7fff11ad","tid":354252,"uid":60814,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:27:09.000Z","msg":"180磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nshe will be safe"},{"pid":"5f2d403fb204e254ee3d45d2a55ec8312308508d","tid":354252,"uid":81737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:31:25.000Z","msg":"會窮"},{"pid":"13d38023f98996136a724e02fbe974301066b03a","tid":354252,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:31:36.000Z","msg":"美少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf007d1d58430d4509d67f357d0f6b4c51aa150","tid":354252,"uid":107623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T09:35:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美少女